Introduction
Introducing Edgemesh® Server: the ultimate e-commerce accelerator for enterprises. While Edgemesh® Client focuses on optimizing site performance through the browser, Edgemesh® Server takes this a step further as a server-side acceleration and optimization platform. With Edgemesh® Server, your website is seamlessly cached at more then 280 edge locations across the globe, guaranteeing fast-lightning access for your customers. Moreover, Edgemesh® Server dynamically fine-tunes your website's resources, delivering highly efficient code to enhance the browsing experience across all browsers and devices. But that's not all, Edgemesh® Server goes beyond performance optimization and offers a range of comprehensive features, including: Search Engine Optimization, Bot and Ad Fraud Protection, and top-tier edge security.
Elevate your online presence with Edgemesh® Server and enjoy unprecedented speed, efficiency, and protection for your business.
